snippet.title: Kirby Gamble Galaxy Stories - Mini Trailer
snippet.description:
Thumbnail by https://twitter.com/DeMeister64

Join our Discord Server: https://discord.gg/qgxUPqv

Kirby Gamble Galaxy Stories is a fangame of HAL Laboratories' Kirby series. It is the most ambitious and biggest Kirby fangame in development with over 20 worlds, lots of Sub-Games, 30+ abilities, including Super Abilities and the newly introduced Mystic Abilities. Go through various different planets and learn the mystery of Gamble and the impending doom that awaits...

Don't forget to drink your apple juice!

Gamejolt Link: https://gamejolt.com/games/kggs/182733
Team Gamble Discord Server: https://discord.gg/qgxUPqv
